'''现代UI'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://msdn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/library/windows/desktop/dd371554(v=vs.85).aspx |title=DirectWrite 简介 |accessdate=2017-01-28 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202084909/https://msdn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/library/windows/desktop/dd371554(v=vs.85).aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|Modern UI}}），也称{{lang|en|Metro UI}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/10/24/clearing-up-the-confusion-its-the-new-windows-8-ui-not-metro-ui/ |title=Clearing Up The Confusion: It’s “The New Windows 8 UI” – Not “Metro UI” |accessdate=2012-12-07 |archive-date=2012-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121127015505/http://techcrunch.com/2012/10/24/clearing-up-the-confusion-its-the-new-windows-8-ui-not-metro-ui/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、{{lang|en|Windows 8 Style UI}}，是[[微软|微软]]一种界面[[设计語言|设计語言]]，已被用于[[Windows_Phone|Windows Phone]]、[[Windows_8|Windows 8]]、[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]、[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]等多款微软产品。<ref name="WindowsPhone7UI">{{Cite web |title=Windows Phone 7 Series UI Design & Interaction Guide |url=http://windowsteamblog.com/windows_phone/b/wpdev/archive/2010/03/18/windows-phone-7-series-ui-design-amp-interaction-guide.aspx |accessdate=2010-10-09 |date=March 18, 2010 |archive-date=2013-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130527071856/http://blogs.windows.com/windows_phone/b/wpdev/archive/2010/03/18/windows-phone-7-series-ui-design-amp-interaction-guide.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.seattlepi.com/microsoft/2011/06/06/e3-xbox-360-getting-tv-tuner-bing-search-metro-interface |title=E3: Xbox 360 getting TV tuner, Bing search, Metro interface |accessdate=2011-06-28 |archive-date=2011-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623112546/http://blog.seattlepi.com/microsoft/2011/06/06/e3-xbox-360-getting-tv-tuner-bing-search-metro-interface/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>採用微软WP为此设计的標準字体。<ref name="WindowsPhone7UI" />在2012年[[Computex_Taipei|Computex Taipei]]大会，[[微软